{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"30af1d9aa9","title":"对《化石》编辑部张锋来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d33861a797","index":0,"year":1975,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"30af1d9aa9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"ac328c990d","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。文元，即姚文元。"},{"id":"22e739739f","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指《化石》杂志编辑部张锋1975年9月6日给毛泽东的一封信。信中说，我是中国科学院古脊椎研究所的一名编辑，科普刊物《化石》创办3年来虽然得到工农兵的初步好评，但却受到出版部门个别负责人的排斤、压制和少数权威的挑剔，至今仍为半年刊，且只有一名编辑。听到中央8月27日关于《动物学杂志》《化石》两刊出大字本的指示后，知道我们的刊物得到了毛主席的关注，社、所已同意改《化石》为季刊，编辑增至4人。信中还对科普工作提出了几点具体意见。毛泽东批阅时，为这封信加了标题“一封诉苦的信”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a691fe9616","type":"title","text":"对《化石》编辑部张锋来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9"},{"id":"ac328c990d","type":"paragraph","text":"小平、文元同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9"},{"id":"22e739739f","type":"paragraph","text":"请考虑，可否将此信印发在京各中央同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9"},{"id":"3406b9aea1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9"},{"id":"582e744007","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9"}],"page":{"id":"1191b56f71","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"30af1d9aa9","start":69,"end":69}}}},"__N_SSG":true}